{"tid":1011201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美財長：美中將在3月1日期限前談成貿易協定","createTime":"2019-02-06T14:49:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-06T14:49:26.000Z","uid":51665,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9f74941ac513cdfecb125a0707f6ad9245f06d57","tid":1011201,"uid":51665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T14:49:26.000Z","msg":"美國財政部長米努勤6日接受CNBC訪問時表示，美國和中國大陸上周在華盛頓達成「重大承諾」，雙方將在3月1日期限前談成貿易協定。不過，他說，現在還有「很多工作要做」。<br />\n<br />\n對於大陸副總理劉鶴上月底的美國行，米努勤說，美國政府和劉鶴進行了「很有建設性的會面」。<br />\n<br />\n米努勤和美國貿易代表賴海哲下周將前往北京。米努勤說，美方將持續推動相關談判，「努力在期限前達成協議，這是我們的目標」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/02/06/realtime/5894431.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F02%2F06%2Frealtime%2F5894431.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=008d2085&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n侵侵又做市<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}